node.text:
Chase your own special light. No matter how hard this situation is, there is always a new light to chase. The light of hope! The light of new friends, of new travels, of new life! Whoever you are, join us, and let's only dream better days ahead. 

Life in a New Light! Within us, all around us! 

#lifeinanewlight #canavesoia #canavesoiamoments #canavesoiaepitome #santorinihotels #hotelvideo 
Special thanks to @needafixer

node.text:
Santorini Comes Alive with the Sound of Music

Canaves Oia leads  the way as Santorini’s most sought-after property, not only due to its impeccable form and idyllic location but most importantly due to its dedicated team.

The video’s slogan, “Luxury Never Sounded So Good,” highlights the key element of hospitality through the power of sound, portraying the staff like an orchestrated band in a fun, energetic and humorous way.
